# Contributing to Flutter Apps

Thank you for your interest in contributing to Flutter Apps!

## How to Contribute

### Adding New Apps
1. Create new app directory with clear name
2. Follow Flutter best practices
3. Use proper project structure
4. Include comprehensive README
5. Add proper documentation
6. Test on both iOS and Android
7. Submit PR with details

### Improving Existing Apps
- UI/UX enhancements
- Performance optimizations
- Bug fixes
- Documentation improvements

## Development Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/sharonaaas27-dev/Flutter-Apps.git
cd Flutter-Apps
flutter pub get
flutter run
```

## Coding Standards

- Follow Dart style guide
- Use const constructors
- Write meaningful comments
- Responsive design
- Cross-platform testing (iOS + Android)
- Proper error handling
- Performance optimization

## Testing

```bash
flutter test
flutter analyze
```

Thank you for contributing! 🚀